  "detailed_description": "Bowling Hills is an exciting golf/bowling mashup! Each lane offers unique hills and hazards to overcome. There's a surprising amount of strategy and skill in this novel bowling experience!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2125190/extras/dc01d501cdebf81d24a57bc58f94e9f2.poster.avif?t=1702326816\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2125190/extras/dc01d501cdebf81d24a57bc58f94e9f2.webm?t=1702326816\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2125190/extras/dc01d501cdebf81d24a57bc58f94e9f2.mp4?t=1702326816\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Ever-Changing Lanes</h2>Tired of bowling on the same, flat lane over and over again? Then the varied lanes of Bowling Hills should be right up your alley! Every frame, the hills and hazards are replaced, forcing you to change your approach.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2125190/extras/cb1db4fa05bf63dd8f7caa01047b0b49.poster.avif?t=1702326816\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2125190/extras/cb1db4fa05bf63dd8f7caa01047b0b49.webm?t=1702326816\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2125190/extras/cb1db4fa05bf63dd8f7caa01047b0b49.mp4?t=1702326816\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2125190/extras/90a6d38111198ca97fc3ec75e0ab60e5.poster.avif?t=1702326816\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2125190/extras/90a6d38111198ca97fc3ec75e0ab60e5.webm?t=1702326816\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2125190/extras/90a6d38111198ca97fc3ec75e0ab60e5.mp4?t=1702326816\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Play with Friends</h2>Bowling is better with company... and competition!  Challenge your friends in person or online!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2125190/extras/35a803f95f8df9c8432d0c7ea9d5b806.poster.avif?t=1702326816\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2125190/extras/35a803f95f8df9c8432d0c7ea9d5b806.webm?t=1702326816\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2125190/extras/35a803f95f8df9c8432d0c7ea9d5b806.mp4?t=1702326816\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Immersive Controls</h2>Your mouse movement controls roll strength, spin, and loft, enabling the finesse required to tackle the challenges presented in each lane.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2125190/extras/a819cf1cc8c8fa19f68c9f801ba1e3e4.poster.avif?t=1702326816\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2125190/extras/a819cf1cc8c8fa19f68c9f801ba1e3e4.webm?t=1702326816\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2125190/extras/a819cf1cc8c8fa19f68c9f801ba1e3e4.mp4?t=1702326816\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>We also support Nintendo Switch Joy-Con motion controls for a more immersive bowling experience!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2125190/extras/e15fb746a2fdc8ebc34ec982d94ab2d0.avif?t=1702326816\" width=616 height=346 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Customization</h2>Bowl in style by selecting the character and ball of your choice!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2125190/extras/ffe59b0fbe1069846fe637e9b6380587.poster.avif?t=1702326816\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2125190/extras/ffe59b0fbe1069846fe637e9b6380587.webm?t=1702326816\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2125190/extras/ffe59b0fbe1069846fe637e9b6380587.mp4?t=1702326816\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Bowling Hills is an exciting golf/bowling mashup! Each lane offers unique hills and hazards to overcome. There's a surprising amount of strategy and skill in this novel bowling experience!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2125190/extras/dc01d501cdebf81d24a57bc58f94e9f2.poster.avif?t=1702326816\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2125190/extras/dc01d501cdebf81d24a57bc58f94e9f2.webm?t=1702326816\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2125190/extras/dc01d501cdebf81d24a57bc58f94e9f2.mp4?t=1702326816\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Ever-Changing Lanes</h2>Tired of bowling on the same, flat lane over and over again? Then the varied lanes of Bowling Hills should be right up your alley! Every frame, the hills and hazards are replaced, forcing you to change your approach.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2125190/extras/cb1db4fa05bf63dd8f7caa01047b0b49.poster.avif?t=1702326816\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2125190/extras/cb1db4fa05bf63dd8f7caa01047b0b49.webm?t=1702326816\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2125190/extras/cb1db4fa05bf63dd8f7caa01047b0b49.mp4?t=1702326816\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2125190/extras/90a6d38111198ca97fc3ec75e0ab60e5.poster.avif?t=1702326816\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"h