ling experience!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2125190/extras/e15fb746a2fdc8ebc34ec982d94ab2d0.avif?t=1702326816\" width=616 height=346 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Customization</h2>Bowl in style by selecting the character and ball of your choice!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2125190/extras/ffe59b0fbe1069846fe637e9b6380587.poster.avif?t=1702326816\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2125190/extras/ffe59b0fbe1069846fe637e9b6380587.webm?t=1702326816\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2125190/extras/ffe59b0fbe1069846fe637e9b6380587.mp4?t=1702326816\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
